---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import MailIcon from "../icons/MailIcon.astro";
import Card from "../components/Card.astro";
---

<Layout title="Mailsite">
  <main class="flex flex-col gap-4 p-4">
    <div class="flex flex-col items-center py-5">
      <h1 class="text-2xl sm:text-4xl font-bold text-center">
        Welcome to Mailsite
      </h1>
      <ul class="flex gap-6 items-center font-bold text-2xl mt-6">
        <li
          class="dark:bg-zinc-800 bg-white border-t dark:border-zinc-700 h-20 w-20 border-transparent rounded-lg shadow dark:shadow-none flex items-center justify-center"
        >
          <MailIcon />
        </li>
      </ul>
      <p class="text-xl mt-6 max-w-prose">
        Messaging solutions for all types businesses
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="container mx-auto">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-4">
        <Card
          title="MailSite Small Businesses"
          body="Simple, yet powerful messaging server for small-to-medium sized (up to 500 employees) companies that want security and reliability at much lower overhead costs. Forget about costly IT administration and time-consuming trainings!"
          href="/"
        />
        <Card
          title="MailSite Large Enterprise"
          body="High-quality messaging server software that provides enterprises with an affordable, secure email, calendar and contacts server with mobile synchronization, calendar server, and advanced security options that can be deployed in a load-balanced cluster of email servers. Learn more!"
          href="/"
        />
        <Card
          title="MailSite Service Provider"
          body="Messaging hosting software that provides carriers, hosting providers and service providers with a secure, clustered, scalable, and fault-tolerant SMTP, POP and IMAP email hosting platform. Learn more!"
          href="/"
        />
      </div>
    </div>

    <div>
      <p class="text-xl italic text-center">
        MailSite Fusion Version 10.4 Released! Mailbox and Domain Administration
        in ExpressPro....
      </p>
    </div>

    <h1 class="text-xl font-bold py-2 text-center">
      ISP-Grade Exchange Alternative Email Server Software with Calendar and
      Contact Sync.
    </h1>
    <p class="text-md mx-5 text-center">
      MailSite Fusion is a windows email, calendar and contact server with
      over-the-air push to all types of smartphones, Full native Outlook sync, a
      sophisticated AJAX web client and a calendar and contact sharing server,
      which can synchronize and publish to many other clients. MailSite has been
      voted in the top 3 mail server products by readers of Windows IT Pro
      Magazine 3 years running.
    </p>

    <h1 class="text-2xl mx-5 px-5 font-bold px-auto py-2 text-left">
      Why MailSite Fusion?
    </h1>
    <p class="mx-5 px-5 pb-9">
      Your email services are critical to your organization. So you need to be
      sure that you select a quality product, from a company with a proven track
      record in communication software. So, why this mail server? Because
      Rockliffe understands your concerns, we have been specializing in
      developing and refining our email server and email security software for
      business and service providers since 1995. Built from the ground up to be
      fast, stable and secure, MailSite Fusion is ready to meet the needs and
      requirements that matter to you most.
    </p>
    <div class="grid gap-4 grid-cols-3 mx-5 px-5">
      <div class="col-span-1 font-bold text-xl">Secure and Reliable</div>
      <div class="col-span-2">
        Synchronized Simple Affordable Scalable Flexible Rockliffe has powerful
        mail security including anti-virus and anti-spam protection, TLS and SSL
        encryption, Sieve Filters, and more! When you buy from Rockliffe, you
        are putting the security and reliability of your email services in safe
        hands.
      </div>
      <div class="col-span-1 font-bold text-xl">Synchronized</div>
      <div class="col-span-2">
        Native two way sync between Outlook, on your desktop, Webmail and your
        Mobile Devices through ActiveSync or using our Collaboration Server
      </div>
      <div class="col-span-1 font-bold text-xl">Simple</div>
      <div class="col-span-2">
        MailSite Fusion is designed to be intuitive software, which is easy to
        set-up, manage and maintain without the need of an IT administrator or
        expensive training.
      </div>
      <div class="col-span-1 font-bold text-xl">Affordable</div>
      <div class="col-span-2">
        MailSite Fusion provides low overhead, low risk rolling upgrades, and
        around-the-clock technical support at a fraction of Microsoft Exchangeâ€™s
        price, making MailSite a great alternative for those who want an
        excellent product at an affordable price.
      </div>
      <div class="col-span-1 font-bold text-xl">Scalable</div>
      <div class="col-span-2">
        For large implementations, MailSite offers unlimited number of servers
        with no added fees or costs!
      </div>
      <div class="col-span-1 font-bold text-xl">Flexible</div>
      <div class="col-span-2">
        MailSite gives you the freedom to customize your own package to meet
        your specific needs! Easily add or remove the options you want to
        incorporate in your subscription.
      </div>
    </div>
  </main>
</Layout>
